# 部门树形结构 get /system/dept/treeselect
```
// 返回值
{"msg":"操作成功","code":200,"data":[{"id":100,"label":"若依科技","children":[{"id":101,"label":"深圳总公司","children":[{"id":103,"label":"研发部门"},{"id":104,"label":"市场部门"},{"id":105,"label":"测试部门"},{"id":106,"label":"财务部门"},{"id":107,"label":"运维部门"}]},{"id":102,"label":"长沙分公司","children":[{"id":108,"label":"市场部门"},{"id":109,"label":"财务部门"}]}]}]}
// sql 
SELECT count(0) FROM sys_user u LEFT JOIN sys_dept d ON u.dept_id = d.dept_id WHERE u.del_flag = '0' 
select d.dept_id, d.parent_id, d.ancestors, d.dept_name, d.order_num, d.leader, d.phone, d.email, d.status, d.del_flag, d.create_by, d.create_time from sys_dept d where d.del_flag = '0' order by d.parent_id, d.order_num
 
```
